title: BSAMCH Notification 2026 - Apply Online for 20 Junior Resident Posts
description: Dr Baba Saheb Ambedkar Hospital and Medical College (BSAMCH) has officially released the notification to fill the vacancies of 20 Junior Resident Posts. Interested and eligibile candidates can use this opportunity to apply for these posts before the last date of application. Candidates who have completed their MBBS can apply for the BSAMCH Notification 2026. The interested applicants can apply in online mode.
